# WhatsApp AI Bot Dashboard

A full-stack WhatsApp business bot with a real-time dashboard. Built with Python (Flask) on the backend and React on the frontend, using the WhatsApp Cloud API and OpenRouter for AI replies.

---

## Features

- Real-time chat dashboard with live WebSocket updates
- AI auto-replies powered by OpenRouter (any model)
- Human / AI mode toggle per user
- Broadcast messages to all users
- File and media sending
- Contact name display
- Unread message badges
- Message search
- User tags and notes
- Analytics dashboard (daily activity, top users, response time)
- Export conversations to CSV
- Knowledge base for AI context
- Duplicate message prevention

