## Setup

### 1. Clone the project

```bash
git clone <your-repo>
cd whatsappbot
```

### 2. Backend setup

```bash
# Create virtual environment (recommended)
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate        # Windows
source venv/bin/activate     # Mac/Linux

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Copy env file and fill in your keys
cp .env.example .env
```

### 3. Frontend setup

```bash
cd dashboard
cp .env.example .env
npm install
```

