## Environment Variables

### Backend `.env`

```
SECRET_KEY=your-long-random-secret-key
DASHBOARD_SECRET=your-dashboard-token

VERIFY_TOKEN=your-whatsapp-verify-token
WHATSAPP_TOKEN=your-whatsapp-bearer-token
PHONE_NUMBER_ID=your-phone-number-id

OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your-openrouter-key
AI_MODEL=meta-llama/llama-3-8b-instruct:free

ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000
FLASK_DEBUG=false
```

### Frontend `dashboard/.env`

```
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:5000
REACT_APP_DASHBOARD_SECRET=your-dashboard-token
```

> `DASHBOARD_SECRET` and `REACT_APP_DASHBOARD_SECRET` must be the same value.

